Title: News: Postgres 15 available in Azure Cosmos DB for PostgreSQL
Description: PostgreSQL 15 major version support is now generally available in the Azure Cosmos DB for PostgreSQL service, within just 1 week of the PostgreSQL 15 release. Powered by Citus open source, Azure Cosmos DB for PostgreSQL gives you true Postgres in a cloud database, with distributed scale.
